                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72111F23/13</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Memorandum of the Counselor for the Department of State</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-01-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 25, 1915</hi>.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Explained orally to the German Ambassador the decision of this Government as to
                    the character of the <hi rend="italic">Farn</hi>, and the treatment she would
                    receive as a naval tender of Germany.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Robert Lansing</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
